21?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational">GIA 3.00ct D-FL</a></strong></td><td>Ideal</td><td>FL</td><td>GIA</td><td><strong>$14,267</strong></td><td>GIA Flawless 3ct pear lab diamond; absolute pinnacle</td></tr></tbody></table>

